skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ninety six country
des:
Here's the greatest of classic country music - top hits generally ranging from about 2000 and back, but with a few modern classics too. This is the KIOX 96.1 FM music stream.

The music has been specially chosen by country lovers in small town Bay City, Texas, and presented to you by genuine country announcers. It also features a great Saturday night listener request call-in show where you can choose the music you want to hear.

To start, just say "Alexa, play ninety six country", or "Alexa, open ninety six country". You can ask Alexa the name of any song by saying "Alexa, ask [invocation term] what's this song?". And, to stop the stream, simply say "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
